tika.dc.description: Lost at Sea features the incredible stories of eight ships and their passengers, some of which vanished with hardly a trace – or no trace at all. Veteran history and mystery writer A.A.Hoehling explores these previously unexplained maritime mishaps with the skill of a detective seeking to uncover a murderer.
